1105
01:09:29,497 --> 01:09:30,562
Where's Murph?

1106
01:09:30,564 --> 01:09:32,232
I don't know.

1107
01:09:32,234 --> 01:09:34,366
[Bartle] Francazino,
where's Murph?

1108
01:09:34,368 --> 01:09:35,367
