1122
01:10:06,467 --> 01:10:07,567
[Sterling] Jesus.

1123
01:10:07,569 --> 01:10:09,369
What was he doing?

1124
01:10:09,371 --> 01:10:10,503
I don't know, he was
fucking hanging back,

1125
01:10:10,505 --> 01:10:11,907
