1141
01:11:15,737 --> 01:11:16,872
That don't mean shit.

1142
01:11:18,539 --> 01:11:19,972
Christ, a drop of
blood in this city

1143
01:11:19,974 --> 01:11:21,377
don't mean a
motherfucking thing.

1144
01:11:24,912 --> 01:11:26,447
